data.description: A charming home nestled in the desirable subdivision of Anthem in Phoenix, AZ. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this 1135 sq. ft. property offers a comfortable and spacious living space. Built in 2003, this home showcases a modern design and features that will make you feel right at home. One of the highlights of this property is its location within a vibrant community. Residents of this lovely neighborhood have access to a fantastic range of amenities, including a pool, clubhouse, and recreation room. Whether you want to take a refreshing dip in the pool on a sunny day or socialize with neighbors in the clubhouse, there are plenty of opportunities for relaxation and entertainment. The home also offers breathtaking mountain views, allowing you to enjoy the beauty of the Arizona.
